09:27: Maula.........

======================================

Maula: The only God (The creator)

Mustafa: Arabic word means The Chosen One
Cognomen/Alias of Prophet Muhammad
widely used for Prophet Muhammad

Murtaza: Arabic word means The Chosen One
Cognomen/Alias of Prophet Muhammad's cousin Ali
widely used for the one who was chosen by God

Haider: Arabic word means Lion. 
Cognomen/Alias of Prophet Muhammad's cousin Ali
widely used for the brave one with highest courage

Ali: Prophet Muhammad's young cousin
Allah (The Only God) has 99 names and Ali is one of them
Ali is an arabic word means The Excellent 
Ali was married to Prophet Muhammad's daughter Fatima

Khair-un-Nisa: Fatima, Prophet Muhammad's daughter
means, Lady Of Peace
Cognomen/Alias of Prophet Muhammad's daughter

Hussain: Prophet Muhammad's grandson
means, beautiful, handsome
Son of Ali and Fatima

Hasan: Prophet Muhammad's grandson
means, beautiful, handsome
Son of Ali and Fatima

======================================

"these very five": Muhammad, Ali Fatima, Hasan, Hussain

God created the whole Universe for them.
